longBusinessSummary: Ezdan Holding Group Q.P.S.C., together with its subsidiaries, operates residential real estate development business in Qatar. It operates through Residential and Commercial Properties, Investments, Hotel and Suites, and Malls segments. The company also develop, own, trade, and rent residential and commercial real estates; and develop and manages shopping malls and commercial centers. In addition, it manage hotel and hotel apartments, and suites and restaurants; and invests in equities of companies in various sectors, including banking, healthcare, and insurance. The company also provides maintenance works, property management, and entertainment services. Ezdan Holding Group Q.P.S.C. was founded in 1960 and is based in Doha, Qatar.
